## Quick start

### Web app (recommended)

```
https://skill-creator.vercel.app
```

No install needed. Open, answer the wizard, download your skill.

---

### CLI via npx

```bash
npx skill-creator
```

This scaffolds `.claude/skills/project-skill.yaml` in your current project directory.

---

### Local development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USER/skill-creator.git
cd skill-creator
npm install
npm run dev
```

Set your API key:

```bash
cp .env.example .env.local
# edit .env.local в†’ ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
```

